quran[8{c,v,t}:
22,31,sirf aik khuda ke ho kar is ke sath shareek nah tehra kar. aur jo shakhs ( kisi ko ) khuda ke sath shareek muqarrar kere to woh goya aisa hai jaisay aasman se gir parre phir is ko parinday uchak le jayen ya howa kisi daur jagah urra kar pheink day
22,32,( yeh hamara hukum hai ) aur jo shakhs adab ki cheezon ki jo khuda ne muqarrar ki hain Azmat rakhay to yeh ( feal ) dilon ki parhaiz gari mein se hai
22,33,un mein aik waqt muqarrar taq tumahray liye faiday hain phir un ko Khana qadeem ( yani beeet allah ) taq pahunchana ( aur zibah hona ) hai
22,34,aur hum ne har aُmt ke liye qurbani ka tareeq muqarrar kardiya hai taakay jo maweshi charpaye khuda ne un ko diye hain ( un ke zibah karne ke waqt ) un par khuda ka naam len. so tumhara mabood aik hi hai to isi ke farmanbardar hojao. aur aajzi karne walon ko khushkhabri suna do
22,35,yeh woh log hain ke jab khuda ka naam liya jata hai to un ke dil dar jatay hain aur jab un par museebat padtee hai to sabr karte hain aur namaz aadaab se parhte hain aur jo ( maal ) hum ne un ko ataa farmaya hai ( is mein se ) ( naik kamon mein ) kharch karte hain
22,36,aur qurbani ke oonton ko bhi hum ne tumahray liye Shaer khuda muqarrarkiya hai. un mein tumahray liye faiday hain. to ( qurbani karne ke waqt ) qitaar bandh kar un par khuda ka naam lau. jab pehlu ke bil gir parrin to un mein se khao aur Qanaat se baith rehne walon aur sawal karne walon ko bhi khilao. is terhan hum ne un ko tumahray zairay farman kardiya hai taakay tum shukar karo
22,37,khuda taq nah unn ka gosht pohanchana hai aur nah khoon. balkay is taq tumhari parhaiz gari pahunchti hai. isi terhan khuda ne un ko tumhara maskhar kar diya hai taakay is baat ke badlay ke is ne tum ko hadaayat bakhsh hai usay buzurgi se yaad karo. aur ( ae paighambar ) naiko karon ko khushkhabri suna do
22,38,khuda to mominon se un ke dushmanon ko htata rehta hai. be shak khuda kisi khayanat karne walay aur kufran Nemat karne walay ko dost nahi rakhta .
